# Backport WebSocket read-callback upload support for Lightpanda.
#
# Base: curl-8_15_0 after patches/curl.patch has been applied.
# Source: selected upstream curl WebSocket changes from curl 8.16 and curl 8.18.
# The core implementation comes from curl 8.16 where CURLOPT_READFUNCTION
# WebSocket upload support and curl_ws_start_frame() were introduced. The
# docs/examples/tests use curl 8.18 wording where practical.
#
# Keep this patch separate from patches/curl.patch so the long-lived
# impersonation delta remains reviewable independently from Lightpanda's
# WebSocket API compatibility backport.

